      "updated": 1772087599243,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Decisions:\n- flow x_ij from depot i to town j\n\nObjective:\n- minimize shipping cost\n\nConstraints:\n- satisfy demand by town\n- depot capacity limits\n\nInterpretation:\n- all depots are available\n- continuous allocation question",
      "fontSize": 24,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Decisions:\n- flow x_ij from depot i to town j\n\nObjective:\n- minimize shipping cost\n\nConstraints:\n- satisfy demand by town\n- depot capacity limits\n\nInterpretation:\n- all depots are available\n- continuous allocation question",
