      "updated": 1772087658066,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "New decisions:\n- binary y_i (open depot or not)\n- flow x_ij remains\n\nObjective:\n- fixed cost + shipping cost (+ shortage penalties)\n\nLinking constraint:\n- sum_j x_ij <= capacity_i * y_i\n\nInterpretation:\n- strategic network design + operations",
      "fontSize": 24,
      "fontFamily": 6,
